}}[[Classes]]: <u>ZChainEndHeart</u><br>
A hook hanging on a chain with a heart impaled on it. It can be combined with [[Classes:ZChainBit32|ZChainBit32]] and [[Classes:ZChainBit64|ZChainBit64]] to form long hanging chains by carefully adjusting the height value of each in the map editor.
